    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been proactively overhauled. The drivetrain utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The chassis is structurally sound with professional subframe reinforcement plates installed to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Every bushing and ball joint remains within factory tolerances, and the OEM Sachs dampers provide the quintessential E46 damping profile. The interior features Nappa leather with pristine bolsters and no dead pixels on the instrument cluster. This is a mechanically sorted, high-revving analog masterpiece for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
